{"tid":2051662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"岑敖暉：悼念本身就是反抗","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:31:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d373bf166066ab32115762382e755a6daeacd3c4","tid":2051662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/3V4LSH4A27VYXIDB7PN7PMTXAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F3V4LSH4A27VYXIDB7PN7PMTXAM%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=3cd1e246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F3V4LSH4A27VYXIDB7PN7PMTXAM%2F&h=b71068cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/3V4LSH4A27VYXIDB7PN7PMTXAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉：悼念本身就是反抗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/unBEX-HjFccSL9sXTAwqOy5xVkE=/802x531/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XC6UN5XEXOTUYA3OKTYFCSEV7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FunBEX-HjFccSL9sXTAwqOy5xVkE%3D%2F802x531%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXC6UN5XEXOTUYA3OKTYFCSEV7U.jpg&h=c67c1322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑敖暉（右）與黃之鋒（左）等到維園參與悼念六四活動。董立華攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】儘管學界近年瀰漫着一片與內地割席的氛圍，不過並非所有年輕一代都不願追憶31年前發生在北京的血腥慘劇。學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉撰文表示，今年他繼續去維園，他解釋：「六四維園悼念，在平常日子或許顯得行禮如儀。然而，在2020年，即一國一制元年，悼念這行為本身就是反抗。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警屯重兵動口不動手  為惡法製和平假象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「或許是最後一次」<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉以「悼念本身就是反抗&mdash;&mdash;香港人終究須迎接這天」為題，討論今年六四去不去維園。他慨嘆說，。。。。。。。。。。。。，或許這是最後一次。<br />\n<br />\n過去數年，年輕人爭論六四集會「行禮如儀」，十年如一，在僵化中失卻抗爭的意義。但岑敖暉說：「這個爭議，我認為在今天已是毫不重要。況且支聯會已經率先帶頭放棄維園的意義，三十年的堅持，敵不過一條限聚令。六四維園悼念，在平常日子或許顯得行禮如儀。然而，在2020年，即一國一制元年，悼念這行為本身就是反抗。」<br />\n<br />\n另一位年輕一代KOL、曾任職立場新聞記者的何桂藍亦指出，經過2019反送中洗禮的香港人，應該更能理解六四不只是狹義的學運：「。。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n何桂藍認為，維園上的一支蠟燭，本就是為了反抗而點燃，「。。。。。。。。。。。」。"},{"pid":"32b175df47526080656d95c137c13504feaf5fe8","tid":2051662,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcb904c08d00cf7e0b8467055196526f7c0ea9fb","tid":2051662,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:20:09.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐幾時變左kol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f15c8ead5d25436abeb96599a57fcd40f1da573","tid":2051662,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"#alexter"},{"pid":"155d3734a5c0c6e70099f240b48ee04701488466","tid":2051662,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"升級係為左證明升級冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}